'''''The Fatal Vision''''' was the name that [[Zhen Mirat]] gave to the ship '''Tine's Future''' after he acquired it from [[Vazan Felix]]. At the time that he acquired it, it was a stock [[KS-500 Spaceways Transport light freighter]], but he modified it so that it held two heavy [[Laser cannon/Legends|laser cannons]], one medium [[Ion cannon/Legends|ion cannon]], and two [[Concussion missile/Legends|concussion missiles]]. It was used as the base of operations for his pirate group, [[The Fatal Visionaries]].

